text: The 1966 Navy Midshipmen football team represented the United States Naval Academy (USNA) during the 1966 NCAA University Division football season. Navy competed as an independent with no conference affiliation. The team was led by second-year head coach Bill Elias. ==Schedule== ==Roster== ==References== Navy Midshipmen Category:Navy Midshipmen football seasons Category:1966 in sports in Maryland
